sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Route as Route<br/>{name}
    participant TLSSvc as Service: {name}-tls<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant InfSvc as InferenceService<br/>(patched)
    participant Storage as PVC or Database

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: User Access to TrustyAI Service

    User->>Router: HTTPS Request<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Router->>Route: Route to {name}
    Route->>TLSSvc: Forward to {name}-tls:443<br/>Reencrypt TLS
    TLSSvc->>OAuth: Forward to oauth-proxy:8443<br/>TLS 1.2+

    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OpenShift OAuth<br/>Subject Access Review<br/>(namespace:{ns}, resource:pods, verb:get)

    alt Authenticated
        OAuth->>TrustyAI: Proxy to localhost:8080<br/>HTTP (plaintext)
        TrustyAI-->>OAuth: Response
        OAuth-->>TLSSvc: HTTPS Response
        TLSSvc-->>Route: HTTPS Response
        Route-->>Router: HTTPS Response
        Router-->>User: HTTPS Response
    else Not Authenticated
        OAuth-->>User: 401 Unauthorized / OAuth Redirect
    end

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 2: Prometheus Metrics Collection

    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant Svc as Service: {name}<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant SM as ServiceMonitor

    Prom->>SM: Discover ServiceMonitor<br/>Interval: 4s
    SM->>Svc: Target: {name}:80/q/metrics
    Prom->>Svc: GET /q/metrics<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Svc->>TrustyAI: Forward to :8080/q/metrics
    TrustyAI-->>Prom: Metrics<br/>(trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir)

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 3: InferenceService to TrustyAI (Model Monitoring)

    InfSvc->>InfSvc: Patched with<br/>MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS config
    InfSvc->>TrustyAI: Send inference payload<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (80/443)<br/>mTLS if in mesh
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Store inference data<br/>PVC (CSV) or Database (JDBC)
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Compute fairness metrics<br/>SPD, DIR

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 4: Operator Reconciliation

    participant Op as TrustyAI Operator
    participant API as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Op->>API: Watch TrustyAIService CRDs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>Op: TrustyAIService events
    Op->>API: Create/Update Managed Resources<br/>(Deployment, Service, Route, etc.)
    API-->>Op: Resource status

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 5: Database Storage (DATABASE Mode)

    TrustyAI->>Storage: JDBC Connection<br/>5432/TCP (PostgreSQL) or 3306/TCP (MariaDB)<br/>TLS 1.2+ (if configured)<br/>Username/Password + CA Cert
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Query results
